title: The Growing Pains of Growing a Creator Business
description:
Sign up for the waiting list for our Online storytelling Course: https://bit.ly/2ZnVCzo
This week we workshop some of the growing pains we're experiencing as a business, it's pretty raw and a bit unplanned. We really just recorded a conversation working through some problems we were trying to solve. Would love hear feedback on this one - tweet at us @colinandsamir
